text: Adrianus "Janus" van Merrienboer (8 October 1894 - 12 October 1947) was an archer from the Netherlands. Van Merrienboer competed at the 1920 Summer Olympics.Janus van Merrienboer == References == Category:1894 births Category:1947 deaths Category:Dutch archers Category:Olympic gold medalists for the Netherlands Category:Sportspeople from North Brabant
